title: Special Episode: Playing the Reopening and Recovery Into 2021
description: On this Special Episode, Chief U.S. Economist Ellen Zentner talks with U.S. Equity Strategist Adam Virgadamo about the path to recovery and mispriced “reopening stocks.”
